title: Luka Doncic, Coach K, and Top-Five Draft Prospects | Upside High
description:
J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks begin the pod by discussing Luka Doncic’s performance against the Utah Jazz on Monday night and coach Mike Krzyzewski’s last home game at Duke (4:40). After the break they each share and debate their top-five player prospects for the next NBA draft (10:26).
Hosts: J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks
Production Assistance: Chris Sutton
